\section{Tokens}

We define a basic notion of tokens as the union of the above ``wrapped'' strings
\begin{code}
data Token
 = TA String
 | TI Identifier
 deriving (Eq,Ord,Show,Read)
pattern ArbTok s = TA s
pattern IdTok i = TI i
\end{code}

